data.description: Quiet, peaceful neighborhood surrounds this classic split-level home on a level 1/4 acre lot.  Oversized primary bedroom with a full ensuite bathroom anchors one end of the main level, while the living room, dining room, and kitchen flow naturally from the sweeping front entryway.  A bedroom and full bathroom complete the main level, with a den/family room, 3rd bedroom, full bathroom and laundry room on the lower level along with access to the 2-car garage.  A half-circle driveway provides plenty of off-street parking, with RV parking alongside the garage.  The fully-fenced back yard contains several fruit trees, a small dog run, and a patio underneath the covered deck.  This home is just waiting for YOUR personal touch!
